Cosmos Commerce is a revolutionary new open source e-commerce platform that specializes in flexibility, simplicity, and scalability. Simply put, each and every aspect of Cosmos is designed with you in mind. You, the merchant. You, the customer. You, the developer. You, the designer. Whether it's our corporate-friendly dual licensing or the versatile plug-in infrastructure, you're sure to find something you love about Cosmos. Take a look around and you'll quickly learn why Cosmos Commerce is the right choice for you and your business.